data.description: Location! Location! Location! Beautiful recently remodeled home in the highly desired gated community of Gabriel’s Overlook. Hidden in Gabriel’s Overlook you will find a community park with access to the San Gabriel River. This home sits on one of the largest lots in the neighborhood, over 2.7 acres with an inviting backyard oasis including a splash deck entry pool. The property includes beautiful heritage oak trees a fire pit and a deck to enjoy the view of the green space. This majestic 2.7 acre property is a rare find in the sought after Liberty Hill School District. Easy access to I-35, Ronald Reagan, and US Highway 183 via Highway 29, making your commute north or south convenient in either direction.
